{"article_id":"r0VBmhI5DQnKPaZo","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"With the California primary election looming Tuesday ,","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"it is still unclear which Democratic candidate will win one of the largest states ' 475 delegates .","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"To hear Hillary Clinton tell it ,","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"she 's on the verge","depth":9},{"id":4,"text":"of beating Bernie Sanders in the Golden State and beyond ,","depth":9},{"id":5,"text":"but the Vermont senator has told supporters","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"that they 're gaining ground ,","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"and stand a strong chance","depth":10},{"id":8,"text":"of cinching the primaries .","depth":10},{"id":9,"text":"In the past few days , Mrs. Clinton has traveled the state in hopes","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"of winning over the the delegates","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"she needs","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"in order to exceed 2,383","depth":10},{"id":13,"text":"and get the nomination .","depth":10},{"id":14,"text":"`` I 'm very proud of the campaign","depth":11},{"id":15,"text":"we 're running here ,","depth":11},{"id":16,"text":"and I believe ,","depth":12},{"id":17,"text":"on Tuesday ,","depth":12},{"id":18,"text":"I will have decisively won the popular vote","depth":12},{"id":19,"text":"and I will have decisively won the pledged delegate majority , ''","depth":12},{"id":20,"text":"she said on CNN 's `` State of the Union .","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"''","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"Senator Sanders ' campaign , however , protests","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"that delegate math and money do n't tell the whole story .","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"He 's not ready to back down","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"- especially with the strong coalition of supporters","depth":11},{"id":26,"text":"he has in California .","depth":11},{"id":27,"text":"`` It is extremely unlikely that Secretary Clinton will have the requisite number of pledged delegates","depth":13},{"id":28,"text":"to claim victory on Tuesday night , ''","depth":13},{"id":29,"text":"Sanders told reporters in Los Angeles on Saturday ,","depth":12},{"id":30,"text":"according to CNN .","depth":11},{"id":31,"text":"`` At the end of the nominating process , no candidate will have enough pledged delegates","depth":13},{"id":32,"text":"to call the campaign a victory .","depth":13},{"id":33,"text":"That will be dependent upon superdelegates .","depth":12},{"id":34,"text":"In other words , the Democratic National Convention will be a contested convention . ''","depth":11},{"id":35,"text":"Some Clinton fans , in particular , fear","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"the continued intra-party fight will risk Democrats ' unity ahead of the general election ,","depth":11},{"id":37,"text":"leaving them vulnerable against presumed Republican nominee Donald Trump .","depth":11},{"id":38,"text":"Even if Clinton wins the nomination ,","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"part of her energy will need to go towards wooing `` Bernie or Bust '' supporters ,","depth":11},{"id":40,"text":"instead of focusing on existing Trump voters alone .","depth":11},{"id":41,"text":"Twenty-five percent of Sanders supporters said","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"they would not vote for Clinton in the general election","depth":11},{"id":43,"text":"if she were the nominee against Trump ,","depth":11},{"id":44,"text":"according to a Quinnipiac University poll .","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"The `` Bernie or Bust '' movement may be even stronger in California ,","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"where the USC Dornsife/LA Times poll indicated","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"that Clinton lagged behind Sanders 43 percent to 44 percent among registered voters .","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"Only 65 percent of those","depth":12},{"id":49,"text":"who are voting Sanders in the California primary","depth":12},{"id":50,"text":"said","depth":11},{"id":51,"text":"they would definitely support Clinton in the case of a Clinton-Trump face off .","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"After Puerto Rico 's primary on Sunday , Clinton holds 1,809 delegates and 548 superdelegates , for a total of 2,357 .","depth":5},{"id":53,"text":"Winning the nomination calls for at least 2,382 .","depth":5},{"id":54,"text":"During the Democratic primaries on Tuesday","depth":6},{"id":55,"text":"( when party voters head to the polls in California , New Jersey , the Dakotas , Montana , and New Mexico )","depth":6},{"id":56,"text":"694 delegates ,","depth":7},{"id":57,"text":"including 475 delegates in California ,","depth":7},{"id":58,"text":"will be at stake .","depth":6},{"id":59,"text":"Get the Monitor Stories","depth":5},{"id":60,"text":"you care about","depth":5},{"id":61,"text":"delivered to your inbox .","depth":4},{"id":62,"text":"By signing up ,","depth":4},{"id":63,"text":"you agree to our Privacy Policy","depth":4},{"id":64,"text":"Sanders also swept through California this past weekend ,","depth":3},{"id":65,"text":"verbally attacking Trump ,","depth":4},{"id":66,"text":"but also telling supporters","depth":5},{"id":67,"text":"the Democratic game was n't over .","depth":5},{"id":68,"text":"If they turn out in force on Tuesday ,","depth":5},{"id":69,"text":"he said ,","depth":5},{"id":70,"text":"he 'll be in a stronger position","depth":5},{"id":71,"text":"to capture superdelegates .","depth":5},{"id":72,"text":"`` If we can win ,","depth":7},{"id":73,"text":"and win big here in California and in the other states , and in Washington D.C. ,","depth":7},{"id":74,"text":"we are going to go into the Democratic convention with enormous momentum , ''","depth":6},{"id":75,"text":"Sanders told listeners during a rally outside the Los Angeles Memorial Coliseum .","depth":5},{"id":76,"text":"`` With your help ,","depth":6},{"id":77,"text":"I believe ,","depth":6},{"id":78,"text":"we will come out with the nomination . ''","depth":5}],"relations":[{"parent":157,"left":142,"right":156,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":142,"left":137,"right